Product Description

Fans can take their Transformers figure collections to the next level with Generations Selects, a fan-dedicated line of figures featuring fan-favorite, special edition characters you can’t find in the main line. This Black Zarak figure is inspired by the original 1988 toy release, based on the Super-God Masterforce cartoon. The figure converts from robot to base mode in 39 steps then to scorpion mode in 33 steps. Figure comes with classic Tyrant Spear and shield accessories, plus shoulder cannon details. Spear accessory breaks apart into pieces that can store on the figure’s sides in scorpion mode. Head of spear accessory attaches to tail in scorpion mode. Shield accessory attaches to figure’s arm in robot mode. This Black Zarak figure’s head converts into a Deluxe-scale figure featuring battle-damage deco. Remove the head of the Deluxe-scale figure and convert to an additional smaller figure. Transformers and all related characters are trademarks of Hasbro.

Important information
